description: Just Another Team's recommendations for Season 20. Recommended for Mouse and Keyboard.
name: Just Another Team's MnK rolls - Season 20

data.description: Personally I see this as the start of an Arc blinding grenade launcher. While Voltshot is interesting on a Grenade Launcher, we already have a Lighweight add clear grenade launcher in Salvagers Salvo - which this wont come close to. Otherwise it’s all about ammo economy and getting other benefits from your GL, which Disruption Break helps with.

Personally I see this as the start of an Arc blinding grenade launcher. Otherwise it’s all about ammo economy and getting other benefits from your GL, which Disruption Break helps with.

I feel sorry for everyone who grinded so hard for Wendigo, since this is a craftable alternative who’s only downside is that it cannot slot Adept Mods - which is no big loss. There is an interesting add clear roll here, but it’s nothing compared to the boss dps roll

A Trace Rifle which shines in both PvE and PvP, with desirable perks for both and a consistent route to acquiring it. Despite recommending Paracasual Affinity as the god perk for PvE, don’t sleep on Incandescent to synergise with various Solar Subclass Fragments
